    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331340/extras/a4acc13ed958f0f1186f98280494eebe.poster.avif?t=1731297670\" width=600 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331340/extras/a4acc13ed958f0f1186f98280494eebe.webm?t=1731297670\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >回归经典玩法＆丰富武将组合</h2>大宇资讯重拾RPG类型游戏的初心，在新引擎技术与传统特色结合的全新力作磅礡登场！<br>《三国战旅：乱世行》是以Unreal Engine 5引擎开发的2.5D横向卷轴RPG类型游戏，以三国题材少见的RPG玩法，结合三国武将搜集要素，让游戏队伍的组合产生更丰富多变的玩法。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331340/extras/d079056dd0d607fe38588baaa494f2b5.poster.avif?t=1731297670\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331340/extras/d079056dd0d607fe38588baaa494f2b5.webm?t=1731297670\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331340/extras/d079056dd0d607fe38588baaa494f2b5.mp4?t=1731297670\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>随着武将入队，发挥各武将的强力技能、制霸战场。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331340/extras/2d968b45898f4ab9ed3ffc764b485c63.poster.avif?t=1731297670\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331340/extras/2d968b45898f4ab9ed3ffc764b485c63.webm?t=1731297670\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331340/extras/2d968b45898f4ab9ed3ffc764b485c63.mp4?t=1731297670\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331340/extras/425572522043df5cc13e95899eefea23.poster.avif?t=1731297670\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331340/extras/425572522043df5cc13e95899eefea23.webm?t=1731297670\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331340/extras/425572522043df5cc13e95899eefea23.mp4?t=1731297670\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >史实改编＆三国殊途</h2>剧情以三国史实为基底进行改编，在董卓入京的动荡不安时局下，因其烧毁洛阳的暴行，低调经商的青年窦辅被卷入战乱。原本会作为难民般逃难的他，却邂逅了被藏匿起来的汉室公主，因此展开了与三国群雄交会的命运，走向风格迥异的路线结局。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331340/extras/37014a80752485d91093041a8dda673a.avif?t=1731297670\" width=600 height=300 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >三国：全新印象</h2>随着故事发展，玩家能透过全新视点感受与过往三国作品截然不同的剧情情节，喜爱三国题材的玩家能从中发现不一样的三国面貌，而初次尝试的玩家也能从剧情体验与印象不同的三国魅力。力求创造不论是否熟悉三国历史的玩家，都能享受其中的游戏。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331340/extras/197405ad5cfca03f7e08fa7442ea1b2c.avif?t=1731297670\" width=600 height=240 /></span>",
